        </textBox>
        <text>
        예: calc.exe,paint.exe
      </text>
      </presentation>
      <presentation id="RestrictRunFromHelp_Comp">
        <textBox refId="RestrictRunFromHelp_Edit">
          <label>실행 파일을 쉼표로 구분하여 입력:</label>
        </textBox>
        <text>
        예: calc.exe,paint.exe
      </text>
      </presentation>
    </presentationTable>
